    "body": "In that case geth uses the predefined bootnodes that are not really useful for your private network. If you want the nodes in your multi node cluster to find each other I would recommend setting up your own bootnode and instruct your geth nodes to use that instead of the predefined ones.\r\n\r\nInstructions can be found [here](https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/wiki/Setting-up-private-network-or-local-cluster#private-network).",
